NK071(du)003:1: // gsang ba snying po'i gtan tshigs rnams kyi zin tho bzhugs //
NK071(du)003:3: phyi nang 'khor 'das chos kun gdod ma'i zhing //
NK071(du)003:4: ye nas rtag khyab rnam kun byang chub pa //
NK071(du)003:5: sku lnga lhun rdzogs rgyal kun ngo bo nyid //
NK071(du)003:6: thog ma'i sangs rgyas kun du bzang por 'dud //
NK071(du)003:7: de la 'dir rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhal snga nas /
NK071(du)003:8: skyes dgu'i blo dang mtshams par theg pa'i rnam grangs
NK071(du)003:9: mang du gsungs pa yang bsdu na dgur 'du ste
NK071(du)003:10: / spyi mdo dgongs pa 'dus pa las //
NK071(du)003:12: dbang bsgyur thabs kyis theg pa'o //
NK071(du)003:13: zhes gsungs pa las skabs su bab sa pa dbang
NK071(du)003:14: bsgyur thabs kyi theg par gsum du byas pa'i rnal
NK071(du)003:15: 'byor pha yi rgyud sde gtso bor ston pa bskyed
NK071(du)003:16: pa ma h+aa yo ga yin la //
NK071(du)003:17: de la rgyud sde dang bsgrub sde gnyis su byas
NK071(du)003:18: pa'i nang tshan rgyud sde chen po tan+t+ra sde bco
NK071(du)003:19: brgyad du gsungs pa'i rtsa ba 'am spyi gzhi lta
NK071(du)003:20: bur gyur pa brgyud gsang ba snying po de kho
NK071(du)003:21: na nyid rnam par nges pa'i rgyal po 'di yin
NK071(du)003:22: la / 'di nyid la sngon gyi 'grel bshad mkhan
NK071(du)003:23: po rnams kyis bzhed pa mi mthun pa mang yang
NK071(du)003:24: la / / kun gyi nang nas mchog tu gyur
NK071(du)003:25: pa bka' sde zur pa yab sras kyi bzhed gzhung
NK071(du)003:26: la / / rnams te / rgyal ba rdo rje
NK071(du)003:27: 'chang chen nas drin chen rtsa ba'i bla ma'i bar
NK071(du)003:28: du byon pa'i snyan rgyud khyad par can yin pa
NK071(du)003:29: sogs sgo du ma nas khyad par du 'phags pas
NK071(du)003:30: theg chen gyi phyogs la blo phyogs shing gsang chen
NK071(du)003:31: gyi don la nges pas rnyed pa rnams nas 'di
NK071(du)003:32: nyid kyi bka' srol mi dor zhing yid bzhin gyi
NK071(du)003:33: nor bu rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mor mchod pa ltar
NK071(du)003:34: bsten cing bskur bsti bya bar rigs so //
NK071(du)003:37: rgyud kun rgyal po gsang ba snying //
NK071(du)003:38: de don rnam par gsal mdzad pa //
NK071(du)003:39: gangs ri'i khrod 'dir gsang bdag nyid //
NK071(du)003:40: dngos snang rgya bo pa tsam zad //
NK071(du)003:42: zur mes dbon gyi bzhed pa khyad par du bstod pa dang /
NK071(du)003:43: ma zad mkhas pa'i dbang phyug du ma nas kyang de skad du basngagasa so //
NK071(du)003:44: de yang kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po'i bzhed pa
NK071(du)003:45: dang mi mthun pa'i khyad par cung zad yod pa
NK071(du)003:47: rgyal ba klong chen pas rdzogs pa a ti yo ga'i ma h+aa ltar bkral ba ni /
NK071(du)003:48: theg pa mchog gi rnal 'byor ba rnams kyis dgongs
NK071(du)003:49: pa'i rtsal byung ste gtan la phab pa yin te
NK071(du)003:50: / dper na karma pa rang byung rdo rjes mtshan
NK071(du)003:51: nyid theg pa rgyud bla ma sogs sngags su bkral
NK071(du)003:52: / ba ltar ro // 'on kyang rgyud sde rnams
NK071(du)003:53: so sor bkral ba la skabs kyi shan ma nor
NK071(du)003:54: bar gzhung gi bstan don sor bzhags su gtan la
NK071(du)003:55: phab dgos pas zur mes dbon gyi lugs bzhin te
NK071(du)003:56: rgyud 'di ni theg dgu so sor byas pa'i bskyed
NK071(du)003:57: pa ma h+aa yo ga nyid yin pa'i phyir ro
NK071(du)003:58: / ba ltar ro // // des na 'di lugs
NK071(du)003:59: kyis gzhung gi bstan don snying por dril na don
NK071(du)003:61: dang po de kho na nyid lta ba ni /
NK071(du)003:62: mtha' gang du'ang ma ltung ba'i sems nyid ye nas
NK071(du)003:63: dag pa'i ngo bo nyid don dam bden pa dang
NK071(du)003:64: / de'i rang rtsal sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor rang snang ba kun rdzob bden pa ste /
NK071(du)003:65: de gnyis zung 'jug dbyer med mnyam pa nyid du gnas shing mtshan 'dzin las 'das pa'o //
NK071(du)003:66: gnyis pa la dor ba spyod pa ni /
NK071(du)003:67: thabs shes khyad par can gyi zin pa'i sgo gsum
NK071(du)003:68: gyi bya ba thun mong dang thun mong ma yin
NK071(du)003:70: gsum pa bkod pa dkyil 'khor ni /
NK071(du)003:71: snod bcud lha yi zhing dang sku yi dkyil 'khor du rdzogs par snang ba ste /
NK071(du)003:72: gzhi lam 'bras gsum gyi rang bzhin du snang ba'i
NK071(du)003:73: dkyil 'khor rnam pa bdun du gsung pa'i phyir ro
NK071(du)003:80: chos mchog gi dkyil 'khor dang bdun no //
NK071(du)003:81: bzhi pa rim par bsgrod pa dbang ni /
NK071(du)003:82: rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhi'i tshogs pa la bsten nas dbang
NK071(du)003:83: bzhi bskur ba'i las kyi go 'phang gi chos brgyud
NK071(du)003:84: la 'jog cing thar ba'i myu gu mngon du skyed
NK071(du)003:85: pa dang skye nges kyi nus rung du smin par
NK071(du)003:86: byed pa ste / slob dpon gsang ba shes rab dang /
NK071(du)003:87: de ma theg pa'i dbang bzhi dang /
NK071(du)003:88: bu dbang la zhi bar phan dbang bcu khro bor nyer brgyad /
NK071(du)003:89: thun mong du nus dbang lnga ste rtsa ba'i dbye ba lnga'o //
NK071(du)003:90: lnga pa mi 'da' ba dam tshig ni /
NK071(du)003:91: bsrung bya'i don khyad par can rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga /
NK071(du)003:92: yan lag bco lnga spros pa'i dam tshig sum brgya
NK071(du)003:93: drug cu sogs las nam yang mi 'da' bar sdom
NK071(du)003:94: pa'i sems pa sa bon dang bcas pa'o //
NK071(du)003:95: drug pa rol ba phrin las ni /
NK071(du)003:96: zur dang po snying rje gzhan don la dmigs pa
NK071(du)003:97: dang zur gnyis pa shes rab rdzogs byang la dmigs
NK071(du)003:98: pa'i thabs mkhas khyad par can gyis zin pa'i zhi
NK071(du)003:99: rgyas dbang drag gi las sna tshogs kyi mdzad spyod
NK071(du)003:100: do // bdun pa don du gnyer bya bsgrub pa ni /
NK071(du)003:101: gzhi phun sum tshogs pa lnga tshang ba dang /
NK071(du)003:102: rkyen bsgrub pa'i yo byad 'dzom pa'i sgo nas bsnyen
NK071(du)003:103: bsgrub bzhi'i thabs kyis bsgrub pas ro long tshe dbang
NK071(du)003:105: phyag rgya chen po mchog gi dngos grub gnyis mngon du byas pa'o //
NK071(du)003:106: brgyad pa mi g.yo ba ting 'dzin ni /
NK071(du)003:107: sgom bya'i don khyad par can bskyed rdzogs gnyis te /
NK071(du)003:108: skye gnas bzhii'i bag chags sbyong ba dang bstun ste /
NK071(du)003:109: cig char ba dang rim gyi ba'i bskyed rim dang /
NK071(du)003:110: thabs lam steng 'og gi sgo la bsten pa dang /
NK071(du)003:111: grol lam zung 'jug gi rnal 'byor dang bstun te
NK071(du)003:112: rim dang cig char gyi bsdus pa'i rnam par mi
NK071(du)003:113: rtog pa'i ting 'dzin rdzogs pa'i rim pa ste /
NK071(du)003:114: de gnyis las mi g.yo bar sems rtse gcig tu gnas pa'o //
NK071(du)003:115: dgu pa gnas su ston mchod pa ni /
NK071(du)003:116: mchod yul bskul zhing mnyes par byas pa la /
NK071(du)003:117: mchod pa'i bsam pa rnam par dag pas sgo gsum dang /
NK071(du)003:119: spyir 'jigs rten dang 'jig rten 'das pa'i mchod pa dang /
NK071(du)003:123: gsang ba sbyor sgrol lam zhi khro'i mchod pa bcu
NK071(du)003:124: bzhi la sogs pas mchod pas mnyes par byas pa'o
NK071(du)003:125: // bcu pa sngags dang phyag rgya ni /
NK071(du)003:126: thabs shes kyi yi ge 'dus shing byin gyis brlabs
NK071(du)003:127: pa'i nus mthu khyad par can du gyur ba ni
NK071(du)003:128: sngags te / de la spyir gsang sngags /
NK071(du)003:129: rig sngags gzungs sngags gsum dang /
NK071(du)003:130: bye brag rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i /
NK071(du)003:132: bzlas pa las kyi sngags so //
NK071(du)003:133: de bzhin du rigs pa phyag rgya bzhi rtogs kyi
NK071(du)003:134: lha'i sku gsal ba las mi 'da' ba ni phyag
NK071(du)003:135: rgya ste / spyir rtog tshogs ye nas lha'i dkyil 'khor du gnas pa rang bzhin /
NK071(du)003:137: de mngon du byas pa 'bras bu'i phyag rgya dang gsum /
NK071(du)003:138: bye brag lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyis dbang du byas na /
NK071(du)003:142: sku nyid kyi phyag rgya dang bzhi'o //
NK071(du)003:143: de ltar don rnam pa bcu'i khog phub pas /
NK071(du)003:144: rgyud 'di yi dbu zhabs kyi don thams cad so
NK071(du)003:145: sor ma 'dres par bde blag tu rtogs par gyur
NK071(du)003:146: bas gnad gal po che rtsa ba'i mdo 'dzin yin
NK071(du)003:147: pas 'di'i tshig don gyi cha blo la byang chub
NK071(du)003:148: par gyis shig / de ltar rgyud kyi bstan don
NK071(du)003:149: de dag so sor byas de gtan la pheb pa
NK071(du)003:150: par gyis shig / la / dbang po rab kyi
NK071(du)003:151: gtan tshigs kyi sgo nas rtogs par bya ba dang
NK071(du)003:152: par gyis shig / la / / dbang 'bring gis
NK071(du)003:153: rang bzhin dang 'bras bu'i rtags la bsten nas rtogs
NK071(du)003:155: dbang po tha ma rnams kyis brgyud de rtogs par bya ba gsum du mchis pa'i /
NK071(du)003:156: dbang po mchog gi ngor bstan pa gtan tshigs kyi sgo nas gzhung don rnam par 'byed pa la /
NK071(du)003:157: gtan tshigs chen po rnam pa bzhi dang /
NK071(du)003:158: khyad par gyi gtan tshigs gcig te rtogs pa bzhi yi gtan tshigs /
NK071(du)003:159: gsang ba bzhi yi gtan tshigs /
NK071(du)003:160: mnyams pa bzhi yi gtan tshigs /
NK071(du)003:161: khyad chos bzhi yi gtan tshigs te bzhi dang /
NK071(du)003:162: khyad par dag pa gsum gyi gtan tshigs dang lngar bsdu'o //
NK071(du)003:163: de la dang po rtog pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs kyis
NK071(du)003:164: rgyud dbu zhabs kyi don thams cad bsdu ba ste
NK071(du)003:165: / log par rtog pa'i sems las 'khor ba dang /
NK071(du)003:166: sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor las myang 'das su snang ba ste /
NK071(du)003:167: de ltar 'khor 'das gnyis su snang zhing zhen pa'i
NK071(du)003:168: chos ni rgyu gcig pa'i sogs kyi rtags kyis gzhal
NK071(du)003:169: bya yin / 'jal tshul snga ma snga ma rgyu
NK071(du)003:170: gcig pa sogs kyis gtan la phab pa'i grub mtha'i
NK071(du)003:171: zhen cha gtan tshigs phyi ma phyi ma yig 'bru'i
NK071(du)003:172: bya yin / tshul gyi dang / byin gyis brlabs pa'i dang /
NK071(du)003:173: mngon sum pa'i gtan tshigs kyi don gyi cha gsal bar bya dgos so //
NK071(du)003:174: de yang ji ltar zhe na /
NK071(du)003:175: yul gyi snang ba ni log rtog gi rgyun snga
NK071(du)003:176: ma nyid la phyi ma nyid spyod pa rmi lam
NK071(du)003:177: gyi snang ba ltar 'khrul bar zad pas na chos
NK071(du)003:178: nyid spros pa dang bral ba las nam yang g.yo
NK071(du)003:179: ba med pa / rba rlabs ji ltar 'phyo yang
NK071(du)003:180: rgya mtsho las g.yo ba med pa lta bu ni
NK071(du)003:181: ba med pa / / rgyu gcig pa'i rtags kyi bsgrub bya ste /
NK071(du)003:183: 'khor 'das kyi bsdus pa'i chos thams cad sems nyid
NK071(du)003:184: rang byung gi ye shes skyes ba med pa'i dbyings
NK071(du)003:185: su rgyu gcig pa yin te /
NK071(du)003:186: de ltar rtogs pa dang ma rtogs pa las 'khor
NK071(du)003:187: 'das gnyis su snang yang spyi gzhi chos kyi dbyings
NK071(du)003:188: su tshul gcig pa'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)003:189: rgyu gcig pa'i gtan tshigs kyis bsgrub pa'i sems nyid
NK071(du)003:190: skye ba med pa'i gdangs las rol ba 'gags med
NK071(du)003:191: lha yi sku gsung thugs su rang snang ba ma
NK071(du)003:192: lus pa gsung yig 'bru'i tshul du snang ba yin
NK071(du)003:193: te / mtshon du med pa'i yi ge a nyid
NK071(du)003:194: mtshon byed yi ge du mar ma 'gags par snang
NK071(du)003:195: bas mtshon nas rtogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)003:196: de ltar rgyu gcig pa'i gtan tshigs kyis rang bzhin skye ba med pa dang /
NK071(du)003:197: gsung yig 'brus gtan tshigs kyis rol ba 'gag med
NK071(du)003:198: gnyis dngos su rtogs pa'i mthus de gnyis ngo bo
NK071(du)003:199: dbyer med du rtogs pa'i byin rlabs shugs la 'byung
NK071(du)003:200: ba yin te // lhag pa don dam dkor bdun
NK071(du)003:201: ngo bo nyid rgyur lhun gyis grub pas de'i snang
NK071(du)003:202: ldog snod bcud sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)003:203: du rang snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)003:204: de ltar byin gyis brlabs pa'i gtan tshigs kyis snod
NK071(du)003:205: bcud sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor rtogs pas
NK071(du)003:206: ye nas gzhi gdangs su rang cher gnas pa mngon
NK071(du)003:207: du gyur zhing rang ngo shes pa la ni mngon
NK071(du)003:208: sum pa'i rtags kyi bsgrub bya yin la /
NK071(du)003:210: bden pa dbyer med gzhi dbyings skye ba med pa
NK071(du)003:211: ni sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor lhun grub
NK071(du)003:213: 'jig rten pa'i blo'i spyod yul las 'das pa'i bdag nyid can mngon sum du rtogs pa yin te /
NK071(du)003:214: blta bya'i yul dang blta byed kyi shes pa gnyis
NK071(du)003:215: su med pa 'phags pa'i so so rang rig pa'i
NK071(du)003:216: ye shes kyi yul med rang gsal mngon sum du
NK071(du)003:218: de ltar rtogs pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs kyis gzhal bas
NK071(du)003:219: 'khor 'das kyi chos rnams sku dang ye shes kyi
NK071(du)003:220: dkyil 'khor du rang snang zhing gzhi chos kyi dbyings
NK071(du)003:221: su rdzogs pas bzang ngan spang len med par mnyam
NK071(du)003:222: pa nyid du rtogs par byed pa'o //
NK071(du)003:223: gnyis pa gsang ba bzhi'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK071(du)003:224: snga ma snga ma bsgrub bya dang phyi ma phyi
NK071(du)003:225: ma sgrub byed kyi tshul du gzhal bar bya ste
NK071(du)003:226: / ji ltar na gzhi dang rol pa gnyis su
NK071(du)003:227: med pa'i gnas lugs ye nas gsang ba'i gtan tshigs
NK071(du)003:228: / te / gnyis su med pa'i chos nyid la
NK071(du)003:229: 'bras bus che ba'i yon thams cad lhun gyis grub
NK071(du)003:230: / te / kyang / de'i don ma rigs pas
NK071(du)003:231: bslad pa'i sems can gyis thog ma med nas ma
NK071(du)003:233: de lta bu'i rol pa 'gag med du snang ba'i
NK071(du)003:234: chos kun sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK071(du)003:235: gnas pa ni rang bzhin gyi gsang ba'i gtan tshigs
NK071(du)003:236: yin te / sna tshogs su snang ba'i chos thams
NK071(du)003:237: cad 'bras bus mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo
NK071(du)003:238: gnas pa la phyin ci log gi shes pas bslad
NK071(du)003:239: nas rang gi rang bzhin ma rtogs pa'i phyir ro
NK071(du)003:240: yin te / // gnas lugs gnyis med spros pa
NK071(du)003:241: dang bral ba'i rang bzhin ni rab tu gsang ba'i
NK071(du)003:243: yul sems dang rgyu 'bras la sogs pa gnyis chos
NK071(du)003:244: thams cad las ngo bo nyid kyi grol te yul
NK071(du)003:245: du byar med kyang ma rtogs pa rnams gnyis su
NK071(du)003:247: gdod ma'i gzhi'i gnas lugs sku dang ye shes kyi
NK071(du)003:248: dkyil 'khor sems nyid las gzhan zhig yod pa ma
NK071(du)003:249: yin pa ni rab tu gsang ba'i gtan tshigs yin
NK071(du)003:250: te / de ltar sems nyid las gzhan zhig gud
NK071(du)003:251: du yod pa min kyang bsgrib gnyis bag chags dang
NK071(du)003:252: bcas pas bsgribs te rang la gab pa gzhan las
NK071(du)003:254: des nas gsang ba bzhi'i gtan tshigs kyis ma rtogs
NK071(du)003:255: pa'i 'gro ba rnams la gsang ba'i bdag nyid du
NK071(du)003:256: gyur bas sngags thun min gyi lam ji bzhin du
NK071(du)003:257: bsgrub pa dang gsal bar byed pa yin te /
NK071(du)003:258: 'di nyid la brten nas don gyis gnas lugs bde blag tu rtogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)003:259: mnyam pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK071(du)003:260: mtshan 'dzin gyi spros pa thams cad spros bral gyi
NK071(du)003:261: klong du mnyam pa bsgrub bya dang sgrub byed thun
NK071(du)003:262: mong dang thun mong ma yin pa gnyis su byas
NK071(du)003:263: zhing / thun mong la'ang don dam mnyam pa'i gtan tshigs dang /
NK071(du)003:264: kun rdzob mnyam pa'i gtan tshigs gnyis /
NK071(du)003:265: thun min la don dam lhag pa'i mnyam pa dang /
NK071(du)003:266: kun rdzob lhag pa'i mnyam pa gnyis te gtan tshigs
NK071(du)003:267: bzhi'i btsal bas gzhal bya'i chos thams cad ro mnyam
NK071(du)003:268: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor du lhun gyis grub cing
NK071(du)003:269: sku dang ye shes kyi zhing gi rol ba las
NK071(du)003:270: ma dag pa'i 'khrul snang thams cad rtogs pas btags
NK071(du)003:271: pa tsam las don du ye nas med pa'i gnas
NK071(du)003:272: lugs rtogs par byed de tshul ji ltar na /
NK071(du)003:273: mtshan nyid theg pas spros pa phyogs re ba chod pa rnam grangs /
NK071(du)003:274: mtha' dag chod pa rnam grangs ma yin pa'ii don dam gnyis su byas pa yang mnyam ste /
NK071(du)003:275: de gnyis gyi ngo bo spros pa bkag pa'i stong nyid tsam du mnyam pa'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)003:276: don byed nus pa yang dag kun rdzob dang /
NK071(du)003:277: don byed mi nus pa log pa'i kun rdzob gnyis
NK071(du)003:278: ga'ang mnyam pa'i bdag nyid yin te kun rdzob tu
NK071(du)003:279: snang tsam du 'dra zhing snang dus nyid nas bden
NK071(du)003:280: pas stong pa yin pa mnyam pa'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)003:281: bzhin du med dgag dang yin dgag gi dbye bas rnam grangs dang /
NK071(du)003:282: rnam grangs ma yin pa'i stong nyid gnyis ga'ang gnas
NK071(du)003:283: lugs don dam gzhi gdangs spros pa dang bral ba'i
NK071(du)003:284: ngo bo nyid lhun gyis grub par mnyam te /
NK071(du)003:285: lhag pa'i don dam skye 'gags gnas gsum dang bral
NK071(du)003:286: ba'i gdong ma'i gnas lugs thig le chen po'i klong
NK071(du)003:287: du thams cad mnyam pa'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)003:288: ma dag pa'i las snang log pa'i kun rdzob dang /
NK071(du)003:289: dag pa lhar snang yang dag kun rdzob gnyis ga'ang dkyil 'khor 'khor lo'i bdag nyid du mnyam te /
NK071(du)003:290: 'khor 'das snod bcud kyi chos thams cad bzang ngan
NK071(du)003:291: rdul tsam yang med par lhag pa kun rdzob sku
NK071(du)003:292: dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du mnyam pa'i phyir
NK071(du)003:293: ro // de ltar mnyam pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs kyis
NK071(du)003:294: chos thams cad sangs rgyas pa'i bdag nyid 'khor 'das
NK071(du)003:295: gnyis med du gtan la phebs par byed do //
NK071(du)003:296: khyad chos bzhi'i gtan tshigs ni /
NK071(du)003:297: rgyud kyi che ba 'don cing khyad par gyi gnad dang dgos pa gsal bar byed pa ste /
NK071(du)003:298: rgyu 'di ni thams cad las mchog tu gyur pa'i rgyal po yin te /
NK071(du)003:299: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad bden gnyis dbyer med
NK071(du)003:300: kyi ngo bo sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor
NK071(du)003:301: lhun gyis grub pa'i sangs rgyas kyi rang mtshan bde
NK071(du)003:302: blag tu rdzogs par byed pa'i rjod byed khyad par
NK071(du)003:303: du 'phags pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)003:304: de ltar rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal por bsgrub pa'i
NK071(du)003:305: gtan tshigs kyis gzhal bas gzhal bya'i rgyud gsang ba
NK071(du)003:306: snying po 'di ni lung thams cad kyi 'byung khungs
NK071(du)003:307: yang yin te / rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa
NK071(du)003:308: dang 'bras bu rdo rje theg pa'i rgyud thams cad
NK071(du)003:309: kyi bstan don gyi snying po thams cad 'dir 'dus
NK071(du)003:310: zhing 'phro gzhir gyur ba'am lung gi spyi 'grel yin
NK071(du)003:311: yang yin te / pa'i phyir ro // ji skad du /
NK071(du)003:313: so sor bstan pa rgya mtsho'i rgyud //
NK071(du)003:315: don kun 'di la yongs rdzogs pas //
NK071(du)003:316: lung gi spyi zhes bshad pa yin //
NK071(du)003:318: de ltar rgyud thams cad kyi spyi gzhir gyur ba
NK071(du)003:319: 'di ni gsang ba las kyang che gsang ba yin
NK071(du)003:320: te / phyogs bcu'i dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas thams cad
NK071(du)003:321: kyi sku gsung thugs kyi gsang ba zab mo las
NK071(du)003:323: de bzhin du gsang ba zab mo'i rgyud 'di ni bgrod pa gcig pu'i lam yin te /
NK071(du)003:324: rgyal ba rdzogs pa'i sangs kyi bstan bya'i chos mdo sngags kyi sgo ji snyed nas zhugs kyang /
NK071(du)003:325: mthar thugs kun gyi 'bras bus bla na med pa'i
NK071(du)003:326: mchog rtsa ba'i rgyud chen po 'dir rdzogs pa'i phyir
NK071(du)003:327: ro // gzhan yang dag pa gsum gyi gtan tshigs
NK071(du)003:328: ni phyi snod kyi 'jig rten sku dang zhing gi
NK071(du)003:329: rang bzhin ye sangs rgyas pa'i bdag nyid yin te
NK071(du)003:330: ro // // bde gshegs yum lnga'i ngo bor nyid
NK071(du)003:331: du 'byung ba lnga rnam par dag pa'i phyir ro
NK071(du)003:332: ro // // // nang bcud kyi sems can /
NK071(du)003:333: rgyal ba thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid du mngon par byang chub pa yin te /
NK071(du)003:334: phung lnga'i rang bzhin bde gshegs rigs lnga'i ngo bor lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK071(du)003:335: rgyud rnam shes kyi khams rnams kyang bsgrib grol ye nas dag pa'i mtshan nyid can yin te /
NK071(du)003:336: tshogs brgyad kyi rol ba thams cad ye shes lnga
NK071(du)003:337: yi rang rtsal 'gags pa med pa'i ngo bor sangs
NK071(du)003:339: de ltar dag pa gsum gyi gtan tshigs kyis snod bcud rgyud gsum la gzhal nas /
NK071(du)003:340: ye nas rnam par dag pa'i rang bzhin skyon dang
NK071(du)003:341: bsgrib pa mtha' dag gis gos ma myong ba'i sku
NK071(du)003:342: dang ye shes kyi ngo bo'i rang bzhin gtan la
NK071(du)003:343: phebs cing / de ltar rtogs pas 'khor 'das snod
NK071(du)003:344: kyi chos ma lus pa rnam par dag pa'i rang
NK071(du)003:345: bzhin sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba chen por ye sangs rgyas
NK071(du)003:346: pa'i bdag nyid kyang shugs kyis rtogs par 'gyur ro
NK071(du)003:347: phebs cing / // de skad du thams cad mchog gi snying po bas /
NK071(du)003:348: gzhan du rgyal bas chos mi btsal zhes so //
NK071(du)003:349: de ltar gzhal bya zhen snang nyid 'jal byed gtan
NK071(du)003:350: tshigs rnams kyis gzhal bas rtogs pa'i lta ba rang
NK071(du)003:351: bzhin gnas lugs kyi don de bzhin nyid de rang
NK071(du)003:352: rig mngon sum gyis yul med rang gsal rjen par
NK071(du)003:353: rtogs pas snod bcud dag mnyam chen por gtan la
NK071(du)003:354: phebs pa'i sngags kyi thun mong ma yin pa ni
NK071(du)003:355: / rgyu mtshan nyid las khyad par du 'phags pa'i rang lugs kyi grub mtha' yin no //
NK071(du)003:356: de ltar grub mtha' la brten nas rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba gtan la phabs pas /
NK071(du)003:357: gnyis snang 'khor chos thams cad gnas lugs bde gsheg
NK071(du)003:358: snying po'i rang gdangs las nam yang g.yo ba med
NK071(du)003:359: pa'i gnad kyis / phyi nang snod bcud rtogs tshogs
NK071(du)003:360: sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang
NK071(du)003:362: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid ting nge 'dzin rtogs gom gyi bag chags yang yang bzhag pas /
NK071(du)003:363: mtshan 'dzin ma rigs pa'i bsgrib pa glo bur ba
NK071(du)003:364: nam mkha' sprin dwangs ba ltar rang sar dag pas
NK071(du)003:365: / lam gyur 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid gsang gsum mi
NK071(du)003:366: zad rgyan gyi yon tan rdzogs te rigs 'dzin bzhi'i
NK071(du)003:368: shin tu rtogs dka' gsang ba snying po'i gnad //
NK071(du)003:369: dpal ldan zur ba'i bka' srol zab mo'i mdzod //
NK071(du)003:370: mthong ba'i rnam par 'byed pa'i blo gter d+harma sh+ri //
NK071(du)003:371: gang gi dpal las zab mo'i gtam 'di byung //
NK071(du)003:372: sku dang ye shes rnam dag bdud rtsis sprin //
NK071(du)003:373: skye dgu'i yid kyi pad mtshor rtag khyab pas //
NK071(du)003:374: mthong ba'i bskal bzang shi li m+au kha rnams //
NK071(du)003:375: rnam par grol ba'i dga' ston 'di gyur cig /
NK071(du)003:376: ces rgyud gsang ba snying po'i gtan tshigs rnams kyi
NK071(du)003:377: zin tho 'di ltar dgos zhes sdom brtson sde snod
NK071(du)003:378: 'dzin pa blo gros rgya mtsho nas bskul ba'i ngor
NK071(du)003:379: kahthoga pa dge rtse 'gyur med bstan pa'i rnam rgyal
NK071(du)003:380: gyis rang lo sum bcu par khrom rgyud ri bo
NK071(du)003:381: che nas shar mar bris pa dag bar gyur cig
